### Connection Management (порт 8090)
### Требует запущенных: groups-channels (8082), chat-history (8083); users (8081) — опц. (presence best-effort)

### --- Реестр соединений (KV) ---

### 1. Зарегистрировать соединение: alice на сервере 8084
PUT http://localhost:8090/internal/connections/alice
Content-Type: application/json

{ "serverUrl": "http://localhost:8084" }

### 2. Зарегистрировать соединение: bob на сервере 8085 (другой сервер!)
PUT http://localhost:8090/internal/connections/bob
Content-Type: application/json

{ "serverUrl": "http://localhost:8085" }

### 3. Снимок реестра userId -> serverUrl
GET http://localhost:8090/internal/connections

### --- Маршрутизация / оркестрация ---

### 4. SEND_DIRECT alice -> bob (lazy-resolve группы, store, fan-out)
# bob зарегистрирован на 8085 (которого нет) -> попадёт в failedDelivery (демонстрация fan-out)
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_DIRECT", "toUserId": "bob", "text": "Привет, Боб!" }

### 5. SEND_DIRECT alice -> carol (carol офлайн, не в реестре -> offline list)
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_DIRECT", "toUserId": "carol", "text": "Привет, Кэрол!" }

### 6. SEND_GROUP в существующую группу (chatId подставить из ответа #4 или из groups-db)
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_GROUP", "chatId": "ЗАМЕНИ_НА_groupId", "text": "Всем привет!" }

### 7. SEND_CHANNEL в существующий канал (chatId = channelId)
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_CHANNEL", "chatId": "ЗАМЕНИ_НА_channelId", "text": "Пост в канал" }

### --- Валидация ---

### 8. SEND_DIRECT без toUserId -> 400 MISSING_TO_USER
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_DIRECT", "text": "нет адресата" }

### 9. SEND_GROUP без chatId -> 400 MISSING_CHAT_ID
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_GROUP", "text": "нет chatId" }

### 10. Пустой text -> 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST http://localhost:8090/internal/messages/route
Content-Type: application/json

{ "senderId": "alice", "type": "SEND_DIRECT", "toUserId": "bob", "text": "" }

### --- Отключение ---

### 11. Отключить alice (presence -> OFFLINE)
DELETE http://localhost:8090/internal/connections/alice
